Introduces Demo.ConsoleAppReactive showcasing advanced reactive patterns with the Ducky.Reactive package. The demo demonstrates real-world scenarios including debounced search, stock price streaming, weather polling, and coordinated notification workflows.
Key features: - Multiple reactive effects (polling, streaming, debouncing, workflow coordination) - State management patterns for counter, search, stock, weather, and notifications - Mock services for realistic data simulation - Error handling and monitoring effects - Interactive console UI with menu system and real-time updates
The demo serves as both a testing ground for reactive features and comprehensive documentation of best practices for using reactive effects in Ducky applications.
